                                    <td>Category ‚ÄúInnovation Sprints‚Äù (90-day rapid trials).</td>
                                    <td>Triangle squads: salesperson + marketer + application scientist.</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
                                    <td class="font-bold">2. Multi-Stakeholder Influence</td>
                                    <td>Map & nurture procurement, finance, sustainability officers via executive round-tables.</td>
                                    <td>Same, but add R&D fellows from global bakery HQs.</td>
                                    <td>Persona-based content, executive briefs, technical white papers.</td>
                                </tr>
