                <div class="card p-4"><h4 class="font-semibold headline">Competitive Response</h4><p class="text-sm">Our advantage comes from execution quality. The competitive moat is built on deep, trust-based relationships forged by our integrated teams.</p></div>
                <div class="card p-4"><h4 class="font-semibold headline">Change Management</h4><p class="text-sm">Success depends on aligning departmental incentives (Marketing, Sales, Tech) to reward shared goals like CLTV and NPS.</p></div>
            </div>
